SAWA (Supporting the Advancement of Women's Achievement) Consulting provides coaching, training, consultative services and technical assistance as it relates to women's achievement and success in the workplace. Customized training, solutions and support are provided by skilled consultants in areas of assessment, coaching, training and ongoing mentorship.

SAWA Consulting was formed to recognize the evolving demands on women in the workforce as they attempt to skillfully straddle personal and professional domains. Evidence suggests that women want to perform and participate in a way that recognizes and respects these factors while allowing them to continue growing, learning and advancing in the workplace.
